text: The Partners is an American sitcom that aired on NBC for 1 season and 20 episodes. It aired from 18 September, 1971 to 1 September, 1972 and starring Don Adams, Rupert Crosse, John Doucette, Dick Van Patten, Robert Karvelas. ==Other websites== * Category:1971 American television series debuts Category:1970s American sitcoms Category:NBC network series Category:1972 television series endings Category:1970s American television series
